measurements.description:
Six well-presented flowers on one  24-cm inflorescence;

	dorsal sepal rolled proximally, light coerulea;
	lateral sepals light coerulea;
	petals ruffled, gently recurved at tips, pronounced midrib, coerulea;


	lip ruffled, notched center of midlobe edge, closed over column, white, throat yellow overlaid coerulea, yellow veins, yellow eyes,
	midlobe unevenly overlaid coerulea, white veins near throat,
	light coerulea picotee;

	substance medium; texture crystalline.
